vent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;en.wikipedia.org&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">doesn&#x2019;t accept a salary</a>, will be severely scaling back his holiday party since Tennessee&#x2019;s economy (along with the other 49 states) is in pretty dire straits. [<a href=\"http://www.tennessean.com/article/20081209/NEWS0201/81209011\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.tennessean.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">Tennessean</a>]</li><li>Not all the Titans are celebrating this week&#x2013;defensive tackle Albert Haynesworth is looking at a 30-day probation sentence for doing 100+ mph on I-65. If he can&#x2019;t keep himself straight during that time, he&#x2019;ll be heading to jail. [<a href=\"http://www.wsmv.com/news/18236599/detail.html?rss=nash&amp;psp=news\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.wsmv.com&apos;]);\">WSMV</a>]</li><li>The Hillsboro High School senior that the Vols have been eyeballing has officially committed to UT, making the first pick of new coach Lane Kiffin. [<a href=\"http://www.tennessean.com/article/20081209/SPORTS07/81209024\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.tennessean.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">Tennessean</a>]</li><li>We only hope that when we&#x2019;re 95, we can still slug full-grown men&#x2026; Just maybe not the one who&#x2019;s carrying us out of a burning house. [<a href=\"http://www.wsmv.com/news/18239163/detail.html?rss=nash&amp;psp=news\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.wsmv.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">WSMV</a>]</li></ul><p><em>Photo by <a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/pr9000/3094823429/in/pool-nashvillest\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.flickr.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">pr9000</a>.</em></p><p>No related posts.</p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<!--END .entry-content .article-->"}